translations: n.多样性；多数（multiplicity 的复数）

sentences.sentence: Notice the application of multiplicities in Figure 11.
sentences.translation: 看一下图11中应用程序的复合度。

sentences.sentence: You'll note that I don't show the reverse multiplicities in Figure 5.4.
sentences.translation: 可能你注意到，在图5.4中，我没有显示反向的一对多关系。

sentences.sentence: A one-to-one association is one in which the maximums of each of its multiplicities are one.
sentences.translation: 一对一关联就是它的每个复合度的最大值都是1的这么一种关系。
